-- Author Abrahamson Discusses History of Home Ownership (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-04-19T13:05:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-19/author-abrahamson-discusses-history-of-home-ownership-audio-.html
Eric John Abrahamson, author of 
"Building Home: Howard F. Ahmanson and the Politics of the 
American Dream," discusses the attitudes and financing of 
American home ownership. Abrahamson talks with Bloomberg's Pimm 
Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 13:28
 